Appendix B provides the following sample documentation:

     Scenario
     Master Scenario Events List (MSEL)
     Message Inject
     Message Inject Tracking Form
     After Action Report.

This sample documentation is designed to be used as a template by those responsible for designing and
developing functional exercise documentation. In addition to the documentation described in this
appendix, a briefing containing the agenda and logistics information should be developed and presented at
the beginning of the exercise.




